ISB international double bass convention 1991

Circus Bassissimus, Paul Ellison, Jorma Katrama & Margit Rahkonen, Miloslav Gajdos with Jitka Gajdosova & Zdenek Mucha, Caroline Emery, Mette Hanskov & Niels Erik Aggesen, Sigi Busch, Arni Egilsson, Josef Niederhammer, Duncan McTier & Kathron Sturrock, Red Nitchell & Fritz Pauer, Exhibitor's breakfast, Duncan McTier, Caroline Emery, Paul Ellison, Rodion Azarkhin & Pamela Lidiard, Wayne Darling & Arni Egilsson, Mette conducts mountain top basses, Francois Rabbath, David Friesen, Prize winners, Young bassists concert, Christian Sutter, John Clayton & Fritz Pauer, Joelle Leandre, Joelle Leandre & Barre Phillips, Barre Phillips & Barry Guy, Mozartabend with Paul Robinson & David Phillips, Klaus Trumpf, Hotel Post, Drums - Bill Elgart.
